{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1683-02_011","@resp":"nbb","head":{"value":"Réponse à l’églogue de Mme Des Houlières","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure Galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", février 1683 [tome 2], p. 11-16","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Tout ce qui part de l’illustre Madame des Houlieres est si achevé, qu’il ne se peut que vous n’ayez esté fortement frapée de l’Eglogue, où elle fait parler Célimene, sur les rigueurs de l’éloignement. Cette Eglogue est dans la seconde Partie de ma Lettre de Septembre. Rien n’est plus touchant, ny plus finement tourné, que tout ce qu’elle dit des inquiétudes de cette aimable Bergere. Il faut qu’à son tour le Berger qu’elle aime, vous fasse paroistre le peu de sujet qu’elle a de craindre son inconstance. C’est un des plus beaux Esprits de Bourgogne, qui sert d’interprete à ses sentimens.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"label":{"#":[{"#":{"value":"REPONSE","id":"/div/quote/label/#[0]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"A L’EGLOGUE","id":"/div/quote/label/#[2]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"DE MADAME","id":"/div/quote/label/#[4]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"DES HOULIERES.","id":"/div/quote/label/#[6]/#"}}]},"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tircis, le plus solitaire","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De nos Bergers amoureux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tircis dont l’unique affaire","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’est que d’aimer, &amp; de plaire","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au cher Objet de ses vœux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Eloigné de Célimene,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vit errant de Plaine en Plaine,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Heureux, si quelques Zéphirs,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour seconder ses desirs,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vont porter à cette Belle,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De ses plus tendres soûpirs","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’haleine pure &amp; fidelle ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Heureux, heureux mille fois,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand dans ces tristes abois,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Couché sur l’herbe fleurie,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nul bruit fâcheux, nulle voix,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’interrompt sa resvérie.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le fidelle souvenir","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De sa Bergere charmante,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Suffit pour l’entretenir ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[19]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A son ame qu’il enchante","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelque autre qui se présente,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il est prest à le bannir.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ny Dorise, ny Lisette,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Perfide, la Coquette,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[24]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il aima si tendrement,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[25]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Son Troupeau, ny sa Houlette,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[26]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ny son Chien, ny sa Musette,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[27]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne peuvent un seul moment","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[28]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Luy servir d’amusement.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[29]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que tout dance, que tout chante,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[30]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que tout rie autour de luy,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[31]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Toûjours la Bergere absente","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[32]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fera son mortel ennuy.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[33]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La fidelle inquiétude","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[34]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont il chérit l’habitude,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[35]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des Lieux les plus fréquentez","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[36]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Luy fait une solitude.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nuls attraits, nulles beautez,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[38]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne troublent la chere idée","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont son ame est possedée,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[40]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Célimene occupe tout.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[41]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La douloureuse souffrance","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[42]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une longue &amp; dure absence,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[43]/#"}},{"#1":{"value":"(","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[44]/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelle épreuve à sa constance ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[44]/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":")","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[44]/#2"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rien n’en peut venir à bout.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[45]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sa tendresse ingénieuse,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[46]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sçait par d’invisibles soins","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[47]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tromper de mille Témoins","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[48]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’attention curieuse.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[49]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout ce qui tend vers les lieux","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[50]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où Célimene respire,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[51]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Berger le suit des yeux.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[52]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que ne voudroit-il point dire !","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[53]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand les Oiseaux de nos Bois,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[54]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des doux accens de leur voix,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[55]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Font entendre le ramage.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[56]/#"}},"Ne chantez pas davantage,",{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Leur dit-il,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[58]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":" petits Oiseaux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[58]/#"}},"Allez tous vers ma Maîtresse,","Inventez des Airs nouveaux.","Allez tous chanter, sans cesse","Parlez-luy de ma tristesse,","Allez tous de sa tendresse","Ranimer les sentimens,","Peut-estre bien languissans.","Belles Eaux de nos Fontaines,","Coulez dans ces vastes Plaines ;","Allez dans ce beau sejour,","Au cher Objet de mes peines","Allez faire vostre cour.","Allez par l’ordre de Flore,","Allez naître sous les pas","De la Belle que j’adore.","Fleurs riantes, vos appas","Ne suffiront pas encore.",{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est ainsi que du Berger","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[76]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’ame vivement blessée,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[77]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Laissant errer sa pensée,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[78]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tâche de se soulager.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[79]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il est fidelle il est tendre ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[80]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais est-il sage d’attendre,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[81]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que Célimene aujourd’huy","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[82]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Soit sensible comme luy ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[83]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Non, non, l’amour qui l’enflâme","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[84]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le devroit moins occuper,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[85]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Puis que Célimene est Femme,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[86]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est assez pour le tromper.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[87]/#"}}]}}}}